summary: Merchant with 10k gold located in Rorikstead that will buy almost anything, even stolen goods.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a pawn shop in Rorikstead. The shop is owned by a baby Dwarven Spider named Sweetie who got tired of living in the Dwemer ruins and decided to move to the country and open a shop.  Sweetie sells a variety of items like books, clothes, armor, jewelry, arrows, weapons, pottery and more.  She has 10k gold and will buy pretty much anything from you, including stolen goods.  

[u]Installation[/u]
Drop and drag .esp file to data folder

[u]Uninstalling[/u]
Delete .esp file from data folder.
author: ZeldaKitten
